{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTML","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>超文件標示語言（<strong>HTML</strong>，HyperText Markup Language）是用於指定網頁結構的描述性語言。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"簡歷","title":"簡歷","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在 1990 年，作為 Tim Berners-Lee 對<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/World_Wide_Web\">網路 <small>(en-US)</small></a>所知的一部分，<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Hypertext\">超文本 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的概念被定義起來了。隔年，Berners-Lee 以 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/SGML\">SGML</a> 的標記為基礎定型起來。<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/IETF\">IETF <small>(en-US)</small></a> 於 1993 年規範了 HTML、並在 1995 年發布 2.0（第二版）。1994 年 Berners-Lee 成立了 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C</a> 以便發展網路。1996 年，W3C 接手 HTML 的工作，並在隔年發布了 HTML 3.2 Recommendation（HTML 3.2 建議）。在 1999 年發布了 HTML 4.0 並在 2000 年成為 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/ISO\">ISO <small>(en-US)</small></a> 標準。</p>\n<p>這段期間，偏好 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/XHTML\">XHTML</a> 的 W3C 幾乎拋棄了 HTML，使得 2004 年一個稱作 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WHATWG\">WHATWG <small>(en-US)</small></a> 的獨立團體成立起來。也因為 WHATWG 的努力，<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML5\">HTML5</a> 的工作持續進行：兩個組織在 2008 年發布了第一份草稿、最終標準則在 2014 年實行。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概念及語法","title":"概念及語法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML 是個以<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Element\">元素</a>構成的純文字文件。元素通常被開啟與關閉的<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Tag\">標籤 <small>(en-US)</small></a>包覆起來。每個標籤都以角括號（<code>&lt;&gt;</code>）作為開始與結束。不過，也有些不包覆任何文件的空標籤（empty or <em>void</em> tag），例如 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>。</p>\n<p>你可以透過<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Attribute\">屬性</a>擴展 HTML 標籤，它能提供附加訊息，以改變瀏覽器的解釋方法：</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/HTML/anatomy-of-an-html-element.png\" alt=\"HTML 元素的結構資訊\" width=\"609\" height=\"181\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>HTML 文件的副檔名通常存為 <code>.htm</code> 或是 <code>.html</code>。它們會放在<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">網頁伺服器</a>上運作、並由<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Browser\">瀏覽器</a>渲染。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入了解","title":"深入了解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"學習_html","title":"學習 HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/HTML\">我們的 HTML 教學</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.codecademy.com/en/tracks/web\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">codecademy.com 的網路課程</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML 的 CSS 文件</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 規範</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"簡歷","id":"簡歷"},{"text":"概念及語法","id":"概念及語法"},{"text":"深入了解","id":"深入了解"}],"summary":"超文件標示語言（HTML，HyperText Markup Language）是用於指定網頁結構的描述性語言。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTML","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTML","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/html","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/html/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML","title":"HTML"}],"pageTitle":"HTML - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}